Description:
Verify that the Intro Page opens correctly
Verify that the Term and Conditions in Guest Mode is displayed correctly
Verify that the Privacy Policy in Guest Mode is displayed correctly
Launch the application on the physical device
Wait for 3 seconds for the app to load

Suite/Test/Step Name: verifyElementExist(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Youre Moments Away FromCustomized Vacation Experiences"), 0)
Description: Verify the text "You are Moments Away From Customized Vacation Experiences" is present
Wait for 3 seconds

Suite/Test/Step Name: text = getText(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Youre Moments Away FromCustomized Vacation Experiences"), 0)
Description: Get the text "You are Moments Away From Customized Vacation Experiences" and print it
Wait for 3 seconds

Suite/Test/Step Name: verifyElementExist(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.Button - Login or Sign Up"), 0)
Description: Verify the "Login or Sign Up" button is present
Wait for 3 seconds
Verify the bottom navigation bar "Home" is present
Wait for 3 seconds
Verify the bottom navigation bar "My Account" is present
Wait for 3 seconds

Suite/Test/Step Name: tap(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Vacation More. Get More"), 0)
Description: Tap on the non-clickable text "Vacation More. Get More"
Wait for 3 seconds
Verify that tapping on "Vacation More. Get More" does not redirect to the next page
Wait for 3 seconds
Verify the text "Explore Westgate Loyalty" is visible
Wait for 3 seconds

Suite/Test/Step Name: tap(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Continue as a Guest"), 0)
Description: Tap on the clickable text "Continue as a Guest"

Suite/Test/Step Name: isElementVisible = waitForElementPresent(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Continue as a Guest"), 10)
Description: Wait for the "Continue as a Guest" element to be present after tapping
Check if the element is visible and log the result
Wait for 5 seconds
Tap on the menu button
Wait for 30 seconds for the menu to open
Tap on the "Terms and Conditions" option in the menu
Wait for 30 seconds for the Terms and Conditions page to load

Suite/Test/Step Name: isElementPresent = verifyElementExist(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.view.View-Terms and conditions web"), 10)
Description: Verify the Terms and Conditions webview is present

Suite/Test/Step Name: assert isElementPresent : "Element 'android.view.View - Terms & Conditions-Webview' does not exist"
Description: Assert that the Terms and Conditions webview exists
Print the result of the element verification
Wait for 30 seconds
Tap on the cancel button to close the webview
Wait for 15 seconds
Tap on the menu button again to open the menu fly-out
Wait for 30 seconds for the menu to open
Tap on the "Privacy Policy" option in the menu
Wait for 30 seconds for the Privacy Policy page to load
Verify the Privacy Policy webview is present

Suite/Test/Step Name: assert isPrivacyElementPresent : "Element 'android.widget.TextView - Privacy Policy-web' does not exist"
Description: Assert that the Privacy Policy webview exists
Print the result of the element verification
Close the application successfully
